<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Truth, Beauty, and Peace</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Feb 22, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Father,
</p>

 <p>
There are days <br></br>
when it seems <br></br>
like I’m creating <br></br>
a minefield with <br></br>
carefully placed <br></br>
hazards of <br></br>
discord, <br></br>
ugliness, <br></br>
and lies.
</p>

 <p>
Help me instead <br></br>
to plant seeds of <br></br>
truth, <br></br>
beauty, <br></br>
and peace; <br></br>
building a place <br></br>
where others can <br></br>
run without care — <br></br></p>

 <p>
Barefoot, <br></br>
with joy, <br></br>
in the fields <br></br>
of the Lord.
</p>


